title: Toggle Tabs View in Qutebrowser
tags: @zettel _method qutebrowser
roam-id: a7c8fb89-ed08-4f0c-8974-58393cb9988b
type: text/markdown

- [[Generate Qutebrowser Config File]]

- put the following inside

  ``` python
  config.bind('tt', 'config-cycle tabs.show always never')
  ```

- restart your browser

- this will make pressing `tt` toggle the tab view
